data.description: This home in located in the scenic Lookout Valley. It was completely renovated. In 2009 all of the siding, plumbing, electrical, windows, insulation, most of the sheetrock, metal roof, porches were replaced. New granite countertops installed July of last year. The master bedroom is very large with a very large walk-in closet. Two storage buildings. Hot and cold water in two locations outside. Fenced in back yard.
